    {
      "turn_id": 2,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "明白了，起点是EdgeNode。这个遥测流需要判断条件吗？比如数据是否有效或者是否需要紧急处理？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "IoT_Industrial_TelemetryStream"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "对，这里要加一个判断节点。遥测流进来后先判断Yes或No，Yes走正常处理流程，No直接到最后的汇聚点。这个判断节点就叫IoT_Industrial_TelemetryStream吧，用菱形表示。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "IoT_Industrial_TelemetryStream"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "好的，我添加了判断节点B，标记为Yes/No分支。Yes分支继续往下，您说正常处理流程包括哪些步骤？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "IoT_Industrial_TelemetryStream"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 5,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "Yes分支先经过一个遥测流处理节点，然后到PLC逻辑控制器，也就是IoT_Industrial_PLC_Logic，这是工业控制的核心。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "IoT_Industrial_TelemetryStream",
        "IoT_Industrial_PLC_Logic"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 6,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "确认一下：C是遥测流处理，D连到E的PLC_Logic。PLC处理完之后数据往哪走？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "IoT_Industrial_TelemetryStream",
        "IoT_Industrial_PLC_Logic"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 7,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "PLC处理后的数据要回到边缘节点做本地预处理，所以E后面接F，还是IoT_Industrial_EdgeNode，但这是另一个处理阶段的节点。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "IoT_Industrial_PLC_Logic",
        "IoT_Industrial_EdgeNode"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 8,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "已添加F节点。继续往后，这个EdgeNode还要再连一个EdgeNode吗？我看到后面还有G。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "IoT_Industrial_EdgeNode"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 9,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "是的，F到G是另一个EdgeNode，代表数据准备上报的阶段。G之后要再产生一个遥测流H，进入MQTT消息队列。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "IoT_Industrial_EdgeNode",
        "IoT_Industrial_TelemetryStream",
        "IoT_Industrial_MQTT_Broker"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
