      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "MQTT Broker分发消息后，J节点是订阅端的EdgeNode，然后要驱动执行器控制器IoT_Industrial_ActuatorController，也就是K节点。",
      "elements_involved": [
